With expertise in trek route development, and brand growth, my focus is on elevating trekking experiences while ensuring safety, environmental responsibility, and community engagement. By integrating modern marketing strategies with traditional Himalayan trekking wisdom, I have helped position Himalayan Hikers as an industry leader.

